# Duplicate Contact Prevention (v1.0 — mandatory)

## Rules

Only these fields detect duplicates:

1. Mobile Number (normalized digits)
2. Email Address (personal or official, case-insensitive)

Do **not** use name, PAN, Aadhaar, GST, company, or any other field.

## Behaviour

On Save / Save & Continue / Save & Exit: if a match exists, show **Potential Duplicate Contact** dialog with Open Existing / Cancel. Never create a second contact. No Continue Anyway in v1.0.

## Service

`checkEcmContactDuplicates` / `assertNoEcmContactDuplicate` in `duplicate-check.ts` — future rules extend this service without redesigning UI.
